    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Wait, \"society has historically lagged behind science\"? That sounds like you're saying the people who disagree are just wrong or uneducated. Aren't there actually a lot of people, including some scientists, who argue that gender is primarily a social construct? Why aren't those perspectives being included in that \"consensus\" you mentioned?",
